Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,THE STRONGEST SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose... the Light of Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke\Nthe Dark Puppetry Aura Decimation Field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That attack was like Dai's Air Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That attack I just used\Nin my desperation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the Aban Style\NSpear Technique, Air Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Air technique that only a true\Nwarrior of justice can use...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was finally able to use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest of the Aban Style Techniques,\Nthe Air technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice called me back from\Nthe allure of the great power of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear this to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even should I die, I shall follow\Nthe will of justice to my last breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! His Aura Storm\Nhasn't completely stopped yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A man's face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His power is even greater than before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare... You dare reveal my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The face I must never reveal to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh come on! I didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's enraged?! The cool and collected\NMystban of all people?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How vital of a secret\Ncould that face hold?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! If I can use Air Strike again...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I use the Aura of Justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your abilities are underdeveloped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What could you possibly do to stop me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The least I can do for King Ban is\Nto unleash suffering worse than hell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,on the people of this country\Nbefore their death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry! Scream! And be torn apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The giant castle isn't moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be keeping it busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Help the leaders escape\Nbefore the enemy finds us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you use\Nall your country's might to face them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You would run?!\NYou would abandon your own country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A country is nothing without its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our survival is our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run! I'll fight until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your vessel and troops\Nwere decimated by that giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mahoton spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They've found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world's strongest sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This sword was forged for Dai.\NThere is no other like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, its name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can be none other than the Sword of Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword that was forged just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it's drawn to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this sword?!\NIt's locked and I can't draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword has a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It chooses when and where it fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That sounds kind of finicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see why soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I can't draw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When you require true power in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sword of Dai will respond\Nto your spirit and break its own seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Mystban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow, have you found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes master. The leaders of the world\Nare in the Grand Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Take Sovereign Rock Castle\Nand slaughter the leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to tell me\Nhow it performs when you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Thank you so much, Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You two as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai... Our son...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do look after Popp for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If he ever gets in the way,\Nfeel free to toss him aside, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp is a lot stronger\Nthan you give him credit for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's using an extra Aura Hand\Non Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As for you, I shall tear you apart\Nby my own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you obsess over just me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I'm awakening to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the Aban Style Air technique\Nthat can vanquish the Dark Aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who might\Nuncover the secret to your face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! You shall not speak another word!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone besides Hyunckel\Ncan break the Aura Hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's you, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, your mastery of Air Slash\Nmakes you the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who can completely cleave my Dark Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's true. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}why with the Knife of Papunica?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were seeking a new sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can that sword endure\Nthe power of a Dragon Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My sword says\Nthat you're not worth showing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Little brat. You and your arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be swallowed and die\Nin my Decimation Field, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Style Sword Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Air Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everybody all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he were to use this power\Nwith his new sword...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with your new sword?!\NIs it incomplete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. This sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His shield is a boomerang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many weapons have you got?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, leave him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed for the Grand Chapel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No ordinary power will work\Nagainst Sovereign Rock Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But with your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your actions are futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really is beginning to learn\Nthe Air technique!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Dai!\NWe can still fight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Leona and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power of the sword\Nthat Ron Berku forged!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shadow, hurry and crush the Grand Chapel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was everyone... Were they all defeated?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, fellow leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Had I known they were this powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have focused on evacuating\Ninstead of facing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one thing to die for my own rashness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but to drag you all into this with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bengana, it's too early to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Giving up before any of us\Nwould be true shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the time to lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's facing that giant with a sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!\NThat's Dai's most powerful sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fool! A sword can't cut a castle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Insolent brat!\NI'll crush you along with the others!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's opening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What happened?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible! You cut through\Nthe Dark Army's Sovereign Rock Castle?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the most powerful sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! With just a normal attack\Nit was like slicing open the sky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would happen\Nif I were to use all of my power?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curse you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open all cannon bays!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reduce him to dust\Nwith the might of Sovereign Rock Castle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dragonic Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's Dragonic Aura is going up his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?! Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The central chamber?!\NRight under this throne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He cut the giant castle in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?! Where's Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A true Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sword of Dai showed its true power\Nand cut Sovereign Rock Castle in half.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enraged, Mystban attacks the party\Nwith his fathomless power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kilban suddenly appears,\Nbut disappears again after taunting Popp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In his anger,\NPopp pursues Kilban only to find...{\i0}
